パッケージ com.shimizukenta.secs.secs2

Implementation package providing SECS-II(SEMI-E5) builder and parser.
  • インタフェースの概要
    インタフェース 説明
    Secs2
    This interface is implementation of SECS-II (SEMI-E5).
    Secs2Builder
    This interface is implements of building SECS-II (SEMI-E5) Data.
  • 列挙型の概要
    列挙 説明
    Secs2Item
    SECS-II Data Item Type.
  • 例外の概要
    例外 説明
    Secs2BuildException 推奨されていません。
    Secs2BytesParseException
    Secs2 bytes parse Exception.
    Secs2Exception
    Secs2 base Exception.
    Secs2IllegalDataFormatException
    Secs2 illegal data format Exception.
    Secs2IndexOutOfBoundsException
    Secs2 index of of bounds Exception.
    Secs2LengthByteOutOfRangeException
    Secs2 length byte out of range Exception.
    Secs2UnsupportedDataFormatException
    Secs2 unsupported data format Exception.
